=== generate synthetic-syntax data ===
K=8 transforms, 350 train / 60 test sentences
example base: 'the forest lost the bottle'
  prefix_zk     -> zkthe zkforest zklost zkthe zkbottle
  suffix_um     -> theum forestum lostum theum bottleum
  reverse       -> eht tserof tsol eht elttob
  double_first  -> tthe fforest llost tthe bbottle
  vowels_zero   -> th0 f0r0st l0st th0 b0ttl0
  bracket       -> [the] [forest] [lost] [the] [bottle]
  caps_bang     -> THE! FOREST! LOST! THE! BOTTLE!
  len_prefix    -> 3the 6forest 4lost 3the 6bottle
